✨Self-awareness is about recognising and understanding your emotions. 

✨Self-regulation, the next step is managing those emotions – particularly the negative ones – effectively. 
✨The third ‘personal’ element, motivation is about your drive to improve and achieve: setting high standards for yourself and working consistently towards your goals.
✨A key interpersonal skill, empathy is the ability to put yourself in someone else’s shoes and see a situation from their perspective. 
✨Often described as a ‘people person’, those who are socially skilled are adept at dealing with others.
